Class ClientWebSocketRoutingLogic

  • java.lang.Object
    • at.irian.ankor.switching.routing.ClientWebSocketRoutingLogic
  • All Implemented Interfaces:
    RoutingLogic

    public class ClientWebSocketRoutingLogic
extends java.lang.Object
implements RoutingLogic
    RoutingLogic that always connects to an external directed WebSocketModelAddress. This RoutingLogic is primarily meant for client nodes that do not themselves support connect requests from outside.
